<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>
    <%= title || 'About - Express Quiz App' %>
  </title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/output.css" />
</head>

<body class="min-h-screen min-w-screen overflow-x-clip">
  <div class="main min-h-screen w-screen bg-background bg-image">
    <!-- Reused Navigation from index.ejs (Simplified) -->
    <nav id="main-nav" class="p-4 gap-2 flex justify-center fixed w-full top-0 z-50">
      <nav
        class="glint bg-primary/50 text-purple-300 flex justify-evenly items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full w-[50%] backdrop-blur-xl">
        <div class="flex grow justify-between text-xl items-center ">
          <a href="/" class="font-ramen translate-y-[3px] text-2xl">S</a>
          <a href="/" class="font-poppins">HOME</a>
          <a href="/quiz" class="font-poppins">QUIZ</a>
          <a href="/quests" class="font-poppins">QUESTS</a>
          <a href="/shop" class="font-poppins">SHOP</a>
          <a href="/about" class="font-poppins text-pink-400 border-b border-pink-400">ABOUT</a>
        </div>
      </nav>
      <nav id="yen-display"
        class="glint bg-primary/50 text-purple-300 flex justify-evenly items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full w-fit backdrop-blur-xl">
        <span class="font-poppins font-bold text-lg">¥ <span id="yen-amount">0</span></span>
      </nav>
      <div class="dropdown dropdown-hover dropdown-center">
        <div tabindex="0" role="button"
          class="glint bg-primary/50 text-purple-300 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full w-12 h-12 backdrop-blur-xl">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke="currentColor" class="size-6">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 1 1-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 7.5 0ZM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0 1 14.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0 1 12 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632Z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <ul tabindex="-1"
          class="dropdown-content menu bg-primary/90 backdrop-blur-md text-purple-300 rounded-box z-[60] w-52 p-2 shadow-2xl mt-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 border border-purple-300/20 before:content-[''] before:absolute before:-top-4 before:h-4 before:w-full">
          <li><a class="hover:bg-purple-500/30 transition-colors text-lg font-bold">
              <%= (locals.user) ? user.username : 'Guest' %>
            </a></li>
          <li class="pointer-events-none">
            <hr class="border-purple-300/10 mt-1">
          </li>
          <li><a href="/statistics" class="hover:bg-purple-500/30 transition-colors text-pink-300">Profile / Statistics</a></li>
          <li><a href="/inventory" class="hover:bg-purple-500/30 transition-colors text-yellow-400">Inventory</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:bg-purple-500/30 transition-colors">Settings</a></li>
          <li class="pointer-events-none">
            <hr class="border-purple-300/10 m-1">
          </li>
          <% if (locals.user) { %>
            <li><a href="/php/logout.php" class="text-pink-400 hover:bg-pink-500/20 transition-colors">Logout</a></li>
            <% } else { %>
              <li><a id="auth-modal-trigger"
                  class="text-pink-400 hover:bg-pink-500/20 transition-colors cursor-pointer">Log
                  In</a></li>
              <% } %>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <!-- <nav id="auth-modal-trigger"
              class="glint bg-primary/50 text-purple-300 flex justify-evenly items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full w-fit aspect-square backdrop-blur-xl cursor-pointer">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke="currentColor" class="size-6">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                      d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 1 1-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 7.5 0ZM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0 1 14.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0 1 12 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632Z" />
              </svg>
          </nav> -->
    </nav>

    <div class="flex w-full min-h-screen pt-24 px-8 justify-center items-center">
      <div
        class="glint bg-primary/80 backdrop-blur-xl p-8 rounded-3xl border border-purple-300/20 max-w-2xl text-purple-300 font-poppins shadow-2xl">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-ramen text-center text-purple-300 mb-6 tracking-wider">About Shitsumon</h1>
        <p class="text-lg mb-8 text-center text-purple-300/90 leading-relaxed">
          Welcome to <span class="text-pink-400 font-bold">Shitsumon</span> (質問), the ultimate testing ground for your
          Anime and Manga knowledge! Prove that you are a true otaku by challenging our extensive trivia database.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div
            class="bg-purple-950/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-purple-300/10 hover:border-pink-500/50 transition-all duration-300 shadow-inner">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-ramen mb-3 text-pink-400 tracking-wide">🧠 Challenging Quizzes</h2>
            <p class="text-purple-300/80 leading-relaxed">
              Dive into a vast database of carefully curated questions. From classic shounen masterpieces to obscure
              slice-of-life gems, there's always a new challenge waiting for you.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div
            class="bg-purple-950/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-purple-300/10 hover:border-yellow-400/50 transition-all duration-300 shadow-inner">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-ramen mb-3 text-yellow-400 tracking-wide">💴 Earn Yen Rewards</h2>
            <p class="text-purple-300/80 leading-relaxed">
              Knowledge pays! For every correct answer, you are rewarded with Yen (¥). The more you know, the richer you
              become. Keep playing to boost your balance.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div
            class="bg-purple-950/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-purple-300/10 hover:border-cyan-400/50 transition-all duration-300 shadow-inner">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-ramen mb-3 text-cyan-400 tracking-wide">🛒 The Shop</h2>
            <p class="text-purple-300/80 leading-relaxed">
              Visit our integrated Shop to spend your hard-earned Yen! Browse through the store and unlock exclusive
              cosmetics and profile features.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div
            class="bg-purple-950/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-purple-300/10 hover:border-green-400/50 transition-all duration-300 shadow-inner">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-ramen mb-3 text-green-400 tracking-wide">💾 Save Your Progress</h2>
            <p class="text-purple-300/80 leading-relaxed">
              Create an account to securely save your stats and Yen balance. Your hard-earned rewards are safely stored
              so you can pick up where you left off at any time!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div
            class="bg-purple-950/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-purple-300/10 hover:border-yellow-400/50 transition-all duration-300 shadow-inner">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-ramen mb-4 text-yellow-400 tracking-wide">OpenTDB API Usage</h2>
            <p class="text-purple-300/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              The quiz uses the OpenTDB public API to fetch live trivia questions and categories. This makes the app dynamic while keeping the question source centralized.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-purple-300/80">
              <li>Requests are sent from the backend to <span class="text-pink-300 font-semibold">https://opentdb.com/api.php</span>.</li>
              <li>Example query: <span class="text-pink-300 font-semibold">/api/quiz/questions?amount=10&type=multiple</span>.</li>
              <li>Categories are loaded from <span class="text-pink-300 font-semibold">/api/quiz/categories</span>.</li>
              <li>Server-side logic handles fetching, parsing, and error handling before returning results to the client.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div
            class="bg-purple-950/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-purple-300/10 hover:border-green-400/50 transition-all duration-300 shadow-inner">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-ramen mb-4 text-green-400 tracking-wide">Developers</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-5 text-purple-300/80">
              <li>
                <span class="block text-xl font-semibold text-purple-100">Bautista, H</span>
                <span class="block">Head Developer</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="block text-xl font-semibold text-purple-100">Parica, JR</span>
                <span class="block">Back End</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="block text-xl font-semibold text-purple-100">Wamil, J</span>
                <span class="block">Back End</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify-center mt-8">
          <a href="/"
            class="glint bg-primary px-10 py-4 font-ramen text-2xl text-purple-300 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-primary/80 transition-all shadow-xl hover:scale-105 duration-300">
            <span class="translate-y-[2px]">Return Home & Play</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script src="/js/yen-utility.js"></script>
</body>

</html>